        <body>       

                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>REV. DR. H. PEREIRA MENDES&#44;<lb/>
                NEW YORK CITY.<lb/>
                64 West 11<lb/></p>
            <p>Dec 7th &#39;88<lb/></p>
            <p>My dear Mr Morais<lb/></p>
            <p>Much as I would like to be<lb/> with you Wednesday week&#44; I cannot&#44; through<lb/> a wedding at which I must officiate next<lb/> on that day&#44; and at 4.30 p.m&#33; &#91;Hebrew&#93;&#45;&#45;<lb/> &#33;&#91;Hebrew&#93;&#45;&#45;Let me however know if I<lb/> shall come after the ceremony&#59; I will<lb/> do so.  The ceremony is in Brooklyn&#44; but<lb/> happily near the Bridge&#44; so that I could<lb/> quickly get to Liberty Street.  Let me know<lb/> what train I could take&#59; that is&#44; I will<lb/> come if you have any reception.  For my object<lb/> would be twofold.  First to be on hand out of<lb/> respect for you&#44; as I told our Parnass last night&#44;<lb/> when&#44; in ignorance for the moment of the Brooklyn<lb/> wedding&#45;&#45;I told him I was going to your daughter&#39;s&#59;<lb/> and to manifest my friendship by participating<lb/> in your rejoicing.  2ndly To be on hand to talk<lb/></p>
            
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>to any people you might suggest&#44; about the Seminary&#44;<lb/> as a word from a strange minister is sometimes<lb/> of some good.<lb/></p>
            <p>Concerning the Seminary&#44; we meet next Sunday<lb/> for further examinations of boys&#44; 2 p.m.  Will you<lb/> come on&#63;  If so&#44; come to dinner 1 p.m.<lb/> Mr Blumenthal I hear has written Dr Drachman<lb/> about undertaking the preceptorship for preparatory<lb/> classes.  What do you think of him&#63;  I have had<lb/> a couple of letters written in &#34;Yiddish&#34; for this week&#39;s<lb/> Yiddish papers&#44; appealing etc.<lb/></p>
            <p>The Talmud Torah School I think&#44; will come in&#59;<lb/> if so&#44; we shall have 16&#45;18 more bright pupils&#45;&#45;<lb/> Dr Wise has these for us.&#45;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>I enclose at Mr Blumenthals request&#44; a note<lb/> for your recent expenses in connection with<lb/> journeys to N Yk. for Seminary.<lb/></p>
            <p>With regard<lb/>
                Yrs Truly<lb/>
                H Pereira Mendes<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
